{"type": "article", "id": 20601, "title": "这位银行家爬上高楼记录下迪拜的这些绝美瞬间", "description": "竟然有几分像上海（浦东）。", "date": "2016-01-12T16:43:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 153, "name": "摄影"}, {"id": 1642, "name": "迪拜"}, {"id": 21981, "name": "Syed Ali Adeel Bukhari"}], "category": 5, "author": 18, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 168, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004332zhx8nD9eO4oRmpiL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150459b2u1oFtNQ3pTGIOg.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261505007uRY4B8FOC3Gr2fi.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span style=\"text-align:left;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\">第一眼看到这些美景时，你也许不会想到它们其实是由一位银行家拍摄的。从 2013 年 5 月到 2015 年 1 月，银行家赛义德·阿里·阿迪尔·布哈里拍下了阿联酋迪拜这个城市各种让人惊艳的瞬间。为了拍到天际线，他有时候甚至在没有得到许可的情况下，偷偷潜入某栋高楼。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150501svnbY5oRDgPaAtkl.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"742\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.68703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004327ZcJ1oBaEW8DHC7V5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004327cEYZVgeI5WMXisBb.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004327ztxMW6v7ZP2adAB3.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004328c8ujodDrqaNW0m4h.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t灯光与云海中的摩天高楼\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004328ojnMWIFKxk9msZzH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060043290rjADqG8lmIBaONf.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004329Za9EQ8Tk4dioOFt2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060043307lUqQwAC8y1dpMcI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004330fMqi63HstWEeJo8R.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>迪拜夜景</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004331bj5fVDPY4gHMlsr2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.63425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\">布哈里利用相机定时功能来了张酷炫的自拍</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}